Bootstrap: library
From: alpine:3.9

%labels
    Author Ian Sealy
    Version 1.8

%post
    apk add --no-cache build-base libpng libpng-dev freetype freetype-dev python3 python3-dev py3-numpy py-numpy-dev
    pip3 install multiqc
    apk del build-base libpng-dev freetype-dev python3-dev py-numpy-dev

%runscript
    /usr/bin/multiqc "$@"

%help
    MultiQC - aggregate results from bioinformatics analyses across many samples into a single report
